OL,3,C'Deeply upsetting': Headteacher
OL,4,Cdefends school after criticism of SEN
OL,5,Cprovision
OL,7,FThe headmaster of a Jersey secondary
OL,8,Fschool says he "is deeply upset" after
OL,9,Fcriticism that its Special Educational
OL,10,FNeeds pupils are not taken care of.
OL,12,FDr Gareth Hughes has personally
OL,13,Fwritten to parents at Victoria College
OL,14,Fafter an anonymous testimony appeared
OL,15,Fin the Jersey Evening Post, citing
OL,16,Funchecked bullying and segregation in
OL,17,Fclasses.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
