FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772052053
OL,3,C'Deeply upsetting': Headteacher
OL,4,Cdefends school after criticism of SEN
OL,5,Cprovision
OL,7,FOne parent alleged there had been
OL,8,F"persistent and targeted physical,
OL,9,Fverbal, mental and online abuse" of
OL,10,Ftheir child who has autism and ADHD.
OL,12,FAnother whose son has ADHD claimed "we
OL,13,Frepeatedly asked for reasonable
OL,14,Fadjustments (...) the default response
OL,15,Fwas removal from class and relocation
OL,16,Faway from his peers."
OL,18,FBoth boys were eventually withdrawn
OL,19,Ffrom the school.
OL,26,@vD@MpmvD@Qpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
