FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772052053
OL,3,C'Deeply upsetting': Headteacher
OL,4,Cdefends school after criticism of SEN
OL,5,Cprovision
OL,7,FIn a letter to parents Dr Gareth
OL,8,FHughes, who has been a headteacher at
OL,9,Fthe school since 2021, said that the
OL,10,Farticle was "deeply upsetting".
OL,12,FHe added: "As a parent of a child with
OL,13,Fvery high-level SEN, I am only too
OL,14,Faware that this is a complex area of
OL,15,Feducation.
OL,17,F"Children's needs are diverse and
OL,18,Frarely straightforward, and effective
OL,19,Fsupport often depends on close
OL,20,Fcollaboration between schools,
OL,21,Ffamilies, CYPES and external services.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772052053
OL,3,C'Deeply upsetting': Headteacher
OL,4,Cdefends school after criticism of SEN
OL,5,Cprovision
OL,7,F"I want to reassure you that our
OL,8,Fcommitment to supporting pupils with
OL,9,Fadditional needs at Victoria College
OL,10,Fremains strong and unchanged."
OL,12,FHe also highlighted concerns around
OL,13,Flocal media coverage which draws on
OL,14,Fanonymised testimony and how this
OL,15,F"cannot capture the careful,
OL,16,Findividualised work that takes place
OL,17,Fevery day.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1772052053
OL,3,C'Deeply upsetting': Headteacher
OL,4,Cdefends school after criticism of SEN
OL,5,Cprovision
OL,7,F"Nor the progress that is being made
OL,8,Fwith our children through openness,
OL,9,Fsustained partnership and trust with
OL,10,Four parents."
OL,12,FDr Hughs closed the letter by saying
OL,13,Fhe would like to offer his "sincere
OL,14,Fthanks to parents who have reached out
OL,15,Fsince the article to offer support and
OL,16,Fsimilar kind words"
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
